rComments: She was a kind prof and made an effort to get us to learn French. She would put us in groups to do reading exercises and such. I liked the class in general but there were times where the lectures made me uninterested; then again, grammatical rules will always be boring.
A great prof. and she seems very into what she teaches. She has great teaching methods and makes sure everyone understands the concepts.
Really didn't teach. She expected you to already know all the concepts and to teach yourself.
